public final LegalContentManagementLegalTransactionNamespace.LglTransDateByKeyFluentHelper select(EntityField<?,LegalContentManagementLegalTransactionNamespace.LglTransDate>... fields)
        Query modifier to limit which field values within an entity get fetched & populated. If this method is never called, then all fields will be fetched & populated. But if this method is called at least once, then only the specified fields will be fetched & populated. Calling this multiple times will combine the set(s) of fields of each call.
        Parameters:
        fields - Fields to fetch & populate. See LglTransDate for available fields.
        Returns:
        The same fluent helper with this query modifier applied.
